* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
* B1700 MIL Test Program 1 — Register Moves and Literals
* Tests: LIT, MOVE, CLEAR, HALT
* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
*
* Expected result: X = H0000FF (255 literal)
*                  Y = H00002A (copy of T before X load)
*                  T = 0 (clobbered: CLEAR L uses 8C which writes 0 to T)
*                  L = 0 (cleared)
*

START       LIT H2A TO T                 * T ← 0x2A (42)
            MOVE T TO Y                  * Y ← T
            LIT HFF TO X                 * X ← 255
            CLEAR L                      * L ← 0
            HALT                         * stop
